eomon/bacon combo.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-681456"><a id="comment-681456"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">reedart</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 20th Aug, 2013</div> </header><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">I tried this recipe tonight, I had no cream but replaced it with natural yoghurt. It was really delicious and very easy to make.
