<div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">I have cooked this several times, and can't fault it - quick, tasty and full of flavour. I'm very non-PC with calories, and don't measure the cream too carefully, but don't be afraid to use the pasta water at the end. A small ladle full is about right, but it is easy enough to add a little bit more.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-140330"><a id="comment-140330"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">duttiep</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 20th Nov, 2012</div> </header><div class="comment__rating-and-report-wrapper"><div class="comment__rating"><div class="rate-widget rate-widget-fivestar clear-block rate-processed"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">2.05</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="off"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="off"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="off"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Really disappointed with this. Halved the recipe except(by mistake) for the chilli and the bacon. Thank goodness as this was the only thing that gave it any flavour. So bland. No taste from the courgettes and mixing egg yolk, Parmesan and cream just gave a 'gloopy' lump which was hard to mix in despite the drop of cooking water!</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-136490">